summary: An ordinance relating to and amending Plat 13W, page 57, of the Official Zoning Map of the City of Seattle, Ordinance 86300, to rezone certain property in Salmon Bay City, Lots 6, 7 and 8, Block 31, Lots 7 to 12 incl., Block 36, located on the south side of No. 50th St. from line 1 lot east of Aurora Ave. to Woodland Park Ave., as Multiple Residence Low Density (RM) Zone.
